gc nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/kmaurinjones/</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"ac ci nq nr ns nt\" role=\"separator\"><span class=\"nu by bn nv nw nx\"></span><span class=\"nu by bn nv nw nx\"></span><span class=\"nu by bn nv nw\"></span></div><div class=\"gj gk gl gm gn\"><div class=\"ac ci\"><div class=\"cp bi fv fw fx fy\"><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq or os ot ou ov bl\" id=\"b4de\">Table of Contents</h2><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"2eba\">Project Introduction</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"ed8c\">Technical Overview</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"3cf7\">Content Discovery and Validation</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"57f0\">Content Processing</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"a732\">AI Artwork Generation</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"57c9\">Web Interface Development</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"49f9\">Implementation Details</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"cde2\">Key Findings</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"8c17\">Conclusion</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"ac ci nq nr ns nt\" role=\"separator\"><span class=\"nu by bn nv nw nx\"></span><span class=\"nu by bn nv nw nx\"></span><span class=\"nu by bn nv nw\"></span></div><div class=\"gj gk gl gm gn\"><div class=\"ac ci\"><div class=\"cp bi fv fw fx fy\"><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq or os ot ou ov bl\" id=\"ca08\">Project Introduction</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"6889\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Joyful Bytes</strong> is a project I\u2019ve developed to transform uplifting news stories into AI-generated artwork. By integrating web scraping, natural language processing, and AI image generation, the project aims to create daily pieces that spread positivity. This article outlines the technical aspects of the project, detailing how data is collected, processed, and transformed into visual art.</p><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob pj od oe of pk oh oi oj pl ol om on pm op oq or pn ot ou ov bl\" id=\"017a\">Technical Overview</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"f3c2\">The project consists of an automated pipeline with four main components:</p><ol class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn po pc pd bl\" id=\"745e\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Content Discovery and Validation</strong></li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn po pc pd bl\" id=\"b5b0\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Content Processing</strong></li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn po pc pd bl\" id=\"daf7\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">AI Artwork Generation</strong></li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn po pc pd bl\" id=\"8c47\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Web Interface Development</strong></li></ol><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob pj od oe of pk oh oi oj pl ol om on pm op oq or pn ot ou ov bl\" id=\"b5c3\">Implementation Details</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"ed6a\">The project\u2019s implementation involves several critical components working together:</p><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"2a69\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">APIs Used</strong>:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"8ff1\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Bing Search API</strong>: For discovering news articles.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"8f2c\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">OpenAI (text and image)</strong>: For content validation, evaluation, and summarization.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"64ef\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Replicate API</strong>: For generating images using the Flux AI Model.</li></ul><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"05c9\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Data Storage</strong>:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"7341\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">JSON Files</strong>: Used for storing mappings between dates, images, summaries, and article links.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"af58\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Image Storage</strong>: Images are saved locally or on cloud storage, referenced by the web interface.</li></ul><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"b651\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Error Handling and Robustness</strong>:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"173f\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Retry Mechanisms</strong>: Implemented for API calls to handle transient errors.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"077a\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Timeouts</strong>: Set for API requests to prevent the system from hanging.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"6a9c\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Logging</strong>: Maintained comprehensive logs for monitoring the pipeline\u2019s performance and troubleshooting.</li></ul><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"be45\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Concurrency and Performance</strong>:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"6191\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Asynchronous Processing</strong>: Content discovery and validation tasks are executed concurrently to improve efficiency.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"5edd\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Caching</strong>: Frequently accessed data is cached to reduce redundant API calls.</li></ul><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob pj od oe of pk oh oi oj pl ol om on pm op oq or pn ot ou ov bl\" id=\"f112\">Content Discovery and Validation</h2><h3 class=\"pp nz gq bg oa pq pr ps oe pt pu pv oi nb pw px py nf pz qa qb nj qc qd qe qf bl\" id=\"d66c\">Web Scraping with Bing Search API</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"5a16\">To automatically discover uplifting news articles, I used the Bing Search API with predefined queries focused on positive news. The search parameters were carefully set:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"87c9\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Queries</strong>: Static queries such as \u201cheartwarming news today\u201d and \u201cinspiring stories\u201d to find relevant articles.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"0fdd\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Freshness</strong>: The freshness parameter was set to retrieve news from the last 24 hours, ensuring the content is up-to-date.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"3453\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">SafeSearch</strong>: SafeSearch is enabled, to filter out inappropriate content. I don\u2019t want to have to deal with removing unsafe content downstream of getting results, so leaving the filtering to the Bing API makes things easier.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"0f26\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Language</strong>: Results were limited to English (setLang: \u201cen-US\u201d) to maintain consistency.</li></ul><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"f233\">After retrieving the search results, simple initial filtering is performed to remove duplicates and irrelevant links.</p><h3 class=\"pp nz gq bg oa pq pr ps oe pt pu pv oi nb pw px py nf pz qa qb nj qc qd qe qf bl\" id=\"4bb2\">Multi-Stage Validation with GPT Models</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"85d7\">To ensure that the content aligns with the project\u2019s positivity criteria, I implemented a multi-stage validation process using various OpenAI GPT models:</p><ol class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn po pc pd bl\" id=\"3ab4\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Content Evaluation</strong>: The GPT model evaluated each article based on specific criteria, such as the absence of political or controversial topics and suitability for visual representation. Each model query returns a dictionary containing a \u2018ranking\u2019 (value between 0\u201310) and \u2018explanation\u2019 (brief string of text explaining the ranking).</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn po pc pd bl\" id=\"3a31\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Quality Assurance</strong>: Articles from unreliable sources or those containing clickbait were filtered out.</li></ol><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"cebe\">This validation ensured that only genuinely uplifting stories were selected for further processing. Using these scores, we can rank the validated search results and choose from them a suitable story.</p><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob pj od oe of pk oh oi oj pl ol om on pm op oq or pn ot ou ov bl\" id=\"b3f3\">Content Processing</h2><h3 class=\"pp nz gq bg oa pq pr ps oe pt pu pv oi nb pw px py nf pz qa qb nj qc qd qe qf bl\" id=\"9a33\">Text Summarization</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"69e5\">With the articles passed the validation stage, in order from highest to lowest ranking, the URL of each story is visited using the <code class=\"de qg qh qi qj b\">requests</code> library, aiming to get all text from the page. If the get request is successful and the content of the page is at least 300 words (this check is done to ensure the page content is actually a text worth summarizing), the page\u2019s content is passed to a GPT model to be summarized in less than 200 words, capturing the key elements of the story while preserving its emotional impact.</p><h3 class=\"pp nz gq bg oa pq pr ps oe pt pu pv oi nb pw px py nf pz qa qb nj qc qd qe qf bl\" id=\"5e6a\">Automated Prompt Engineering</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"28b3\">A GPT model is then used to create a prompt suitable for the AI image generation model, specifically doing the following:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"548e\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Extraction of Key Elements</strong>: Identifying visual elements, characters, and settings described in the summary.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"04ce\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Incorporation of Style Guidelines</strong>: Including specific instructions to match the desired art style, such as composition, color schemes, and emotional tone.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"a41d\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Format Standardization</strong>: Prompts were structured in a consistent format to facilitate effective image generation.</li></ul><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob pj od oe of pk oh oi oj pl ol om on pm op oq or pn ot ou ov bl\" id=\"6bc7\">AI Artwork Generation</h2><h3 class=\"pp nz gq bg oa pq pr ps oe pt pu pv oi nb pw px py nf pz qa qb nj qc qd qe qf bl\" id=\"896c\">Using Replicate API with Flux AI Model</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"052e\">For the image generation process, I utilized the <a class=\"ah np\" href=\"https://replicate.com/black-forest-labs/flux-1.1-pro\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Flux 1.1 Pro</a> via the Replicate API:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"2b68\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Model Selection</strong>: I chose this Flux model for its ability to produce high-quality, stylized images that aligned with the project\u2019s aesthetic goals.</li></ul><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"38d8\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Parameter Configuration</strong>:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"afca\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Aspect Ratio</strong>: Set to \u201c16:9\u201d to maintain consistency across all images, best suited for landscape-oriented devices and platforms.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"4ee4\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Output Format</strong>: Used \u201cPNG\u201d for its lossless compression, ensuring image quality. Additionally, of the three file types the Replicate image API can return (PNG, JPG, and Webp), Streamlit can only render PNG and JPG.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"cb86\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Safety Tolerance</strong>: Adjusted settings to comply with content standards and avoid inappropriate imagery.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"62f7\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Prompt Upsampling</strong>: Enabled to enhance image details based on the prompt.</li></ul><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"77cc\">The prompt generated in the previous stage is now sent to the model, producing the corresponding artwork.</p><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"f90b\">For example, the AI-generated prompt\u2026</p><blockquote class=\"qk ql qm\"><p class=\"mq mr no ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"c2c8\">\u201cThe scene shows Surbhi Jain alone on Diwali, expressing loneliness with clear, minimal ink brush lines and gentle gray watercolor shading. Diverse characters are present: Ramesh, an empathetic delivery agent with an exaggerated smile, delivers food to her, bringing warmth to her day. Surrounding them are subtle non-human elements like Diwali lamps and simple plant decorations, drawn with casual, sketchy lines. The composition is centered with ample white space, clean white background, and light gray wash shadows adding depth. All characters have slightly exaggerated features for a touch of humor. Technical details include high-resolution quality, crisp lines with natural brush texture, and a subtle paper texture in the background.\u201d</p></blockquote><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"e128\">\u2026generated the following image:</p><figure class=\"qn qo qp qq qr mf lx ly paragraph-image\"><div class=\"mg mh eo mi bi mj\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"lx ly lz\"><picture><source sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 1400w\" type=\"image/webp\"/><source data-testid=\"og\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/0*yjE_whtX_qKc1Ri-.png 1400w\"/><img alt=\"\" class=\"bi lh mk c\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"presentation\" width=\"700\"/></picture></div></div><figcaption class=\"ml mm mn lx ly mo mp bg b bh ab ee\">Example of Flux 1.1 Pro-generated image, prompted by an AI-generated prompt</figcaption></figure><h3 class=\"pp nz gq bg oa pq pr ps oe pt pu pv oi nb pw px py nf pz qa qb nj qc qd qe qf bl\" id=\"d262\">Quality Control Measures</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"ebec\">To maintain a high standard of visual content, I implemented quality validation for the generated image, using a GPT-4o model call \u2014 with its multimodality \u2014 to evaluate the quality of the generated image according to a handful of criteria about image coherency, thematic consistency with the prompt, and text accuracy and legibility (where applicable).</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"a1c0\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Automated Checks</strong>: Images were evaluated for resolution, relevance to the prompt, absence of artifacts, etc.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"aeaa\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Automated Re-Prompting to Improve Results</strong>: Since the image validation model response is a dictionary of <em class=\"no\">{criteria : 0\u201310 rating} </em>pairs, is the overall rating does not pass the minimum threshold score, the ratings dictionary is added as feedback to the original image generation prompt and used to re-prompt the Flux model, intended to resolve the issues of the previous generation.</li></ul><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob pj od oe of pk oh oi oj pl ol om on pm op oq or pn ot ou ov bl\" id=\"6971\">Web Interface Development</h2><h3 class=\"pp nz gq bg oa pq pr ps oe pt pu pv oi nb pw px py nf pz qa qb nj qc qd qe qf bl\" id=\"8a59\">Building with Streamlit</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"8670\">The final component of the project was the development of a user-friendly web interface using Streamlit, to provide an accessible platform for users to view the AI-generated artwork and the corresponding uplifting stories.</p><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"771a\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Features</strong>:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"0845\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Date-Based Navigation</strong>: Users can select specific dates to view content from that day.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"e574\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Responsive Design</strong>: The interface is optimized for various devices, including desktops, tablets, and smartphones.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"c7c6\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Content Display</strong>: Each page presents the image, story summary, and a link to the original news article.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"b6b4\"><strong class=\"ms gr\"><em class=\"no\">Note:</em></strong><em class=\"no\"> The current feature set in this app will change over time as I receive feedback and make improvements. This description is based on the simplified state at which I\u2019ve initially deployed the app.</em></li></ul><h3 class=\"pp nz gq bg oa pq pr ps oe pt pu pv oi nb pw px py nf pz qa qb nj qc qd qe qf bl\" id=\"a6a9\">Integration and Deployment</h3><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"2b8d\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Data Handling</strong>: The content is dynamically loaded from JSON files, which store the images and summaries mapped to their respective dates.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"0087\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Deployment</strong>: The application is deployed using Streamlit Cloud to ensure high availability and scalability.</li></ul><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob pj od oe of pk oh oi oj pl ol om on pm op oq or pn ot ou ov bl\" id=\"3681\">Key Findings</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"0149\">Throughout the development of <strong class=\"ms gr\">Joyful Bytes</strong>, these overarching ideas proved the most successful to the development of the project:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"abf6\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Effectiveness of Multi-Stage Validation</strong>: Implementing layered validation significantly improved the quality of the selected stories, ensuring that the content consistently aligns with the project\u2019s positivity criteria.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"c7ae\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Importance of Prompt Engineering</strong>: Careful crafting of prompts directly influenced the quality of the generated images. Including specific style guidelines and visual elements led to more accurate and aesthetically pleasing results.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"18d4\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Automation Benefits</strong>: Automating the entire pipeline, attempting to catch errors as often as possible in the development process enables daily content updates without manual intervention, making the project scalable and sustainable.</li><li class=\"mq mr gq ms b mt pe mv mw mx pf mz na nb pg nd ne nf ph nh ni nj pi nl nm nn pb pc pd bl\" id=\"fa75\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">User Engagement</strong>: Providing a simple and intuitive interface enhanced user experience, encouraging visitors to explore more content.</li></ul><h2 class=\"ny nz gq bg oa ob pj od oe of pk oh oi oj pl ol om on pm op oq or pn ot ou ov bl\" id=\"43b0\">Conclusion</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt ow mv mw mx ox mz na nb oy nd ne nf oz nh ni nj pa nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"ea2e\">Working on <strong class=\"ms gr\">Joyful Bytes</strong> has been a rewarding experience, combining technical challenges with a meaningful goal. The project underscores the capability of AI not just as a tool for efficiency but also as a medium for creativity and positive impact.</p><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"1214\">I hope this detailed overview provides valuable insights into the project\u2019s workings might inspire you to explore similar interdisciplinary projects.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"ac ci nq nr ns nt\" role=\"separator\"><span class=\"nu by bn nv nw nx\"></span><span class=\"nu by bn nv nw nx\"></span><span class=\"nu by bn nv nw\"></span></div><div class=\"gj gk gl gm gn\"><div class=\"ac ci\"><div class=\"cp bi fv fw fx fy\"><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"3c83\"><em class=\"no\">Thank you for reading! Feel free to explore the project repository for more details or to contribute.</em></p><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"c71e\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">GitHub Repository</strong>: <a class=\"ah np\" href=\"https://github.com/kmaurinjones/JoyfulBytes\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/kmaurinjones/JoyfulBytes</a></p><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"28a0\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">Deployed Web App</strong>: <a class=\"ah np\" href=\"https://joyfulbytes.streamlit.app/\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">https://joyfulbytes.streamlit.app/</a></p><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"14f2\"><strong class=\"ms gr\">LinkedIn</strong>: <a class=\"ah np\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kmaurinjones/\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/kmaurinjones/</a></p><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mq mr gq ms b mt mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn gj bl\" id=\"40e6\"><em class=\"no\">Spreading digital joy, one byte at a time!</em> \ud83c\udfa8\u2728</p></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></article>"}
